title: Killers Amongst Us: Real Life "Hell's Kitchen," Gorgeous Restauranteur Disappears.  What happened to Dawn?
itunes:title: Killers Amongst Us: Real Life "Hell's Kitchen," Gorgeous Restauranteur Disappears.  What happened to Dawn?
description:
Dawn is a beautiful, vivacious front-end hostess when she meets the man of her dreams, David Viens. He is the chef of a popular eatery. The couple marry and set out to forge their own mark in the food industry. They settle down in California, opening their own very popular restaurant. But one day, Dawn disappears. What happened?
